# DepthGuard — Bright Data + AI/ML API
# Hackathon promo code "unlocked" at brightdata.com → Billing

# ── REQUIRED: SERP API only is enough to win (1 Bright Data product minimum) ──
BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY=
BRIGHTDATA_SERP_ZONE=serp_api1

# ── OPTIONAL: needs payment method on Bright Data account ──
